posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Centerline', 'Our touring schedules and operating hours may vary as we continue to follow local phased opening guidelines and direction from local health officials.', 'Please visit our community website for up to date information.', 'Experience Seattle living at Centerline.', 'With substantial first floor retail, a private/public interior courtyard, roof-top decks with dog areas, BBQ and green roofs bring a real community feeling to the building.', "At Centerline you're right at home.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 215', 'OR Text', '215', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 505 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Wood-Style Flooring', '- Generous Closets', '- Floor-to-Ceiling Windows', '- Modern Kitchens', '- Brand New Apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- Parking Garage', '- Green Roofs', '- Interior Courtyard', '- Rooftop Decks & BBQ Areas', '- Ground Floor Retail', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Centerline', '1420 NE 65th', 'St, Seattle, WA, 98115', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'iv55fSJM6B']
